    • Annotation

      public Annotation(@NotNull Class<?> projectMain, @NotNull String annotationName) throws IOException
      This constructor creates annotations with the chosen name in the package retrieved from projectMain + "annotations"
      Parameters:
      projectMain - the main class in your project. It must be marked with @AnnotationConstructor
      annotationName - name of annotation
      Throws:
      IOException - Needed for files operation, just add the same for the method where the annotation is creating

    • Annotation

      Parameters:

      annotationName - name of annotation

      IOException - Needed for files operation, just add the same for the method where the annotation is creating
